verses.text:
Yea, he loveth the <i>[c]</i>people;
All <i>[d]</i>his saints are in thy hand:
 And they sat down at thy feet;
  <i>[e]</i>shall receive of thy words.

¶ And of Levi he said,¶   Thy Thummim and thy Urim are with <i>[j]</i>thy godly one,
    Whom thou didst prove at Massah,
    With whom thou didst strive at the waters of Meribah;

¶ Of Benjamin he said,¶     The beloved of Jehovah shall dwell in safety by him;
    He covereth him all the day long,
    And he dwelleth between his shoulders.

And he <i>[p]</i>provided the first part for himself,
For there was <i>[q]</i>the lawgiver’s portion reserved;
 And he came <i>[r]</i> the heads of the people;
   He executed the righteousness of Jehovah,
   And his ordinances with Israel.

¶ And of Asher he said,¶   Blessed be Asher <i>[t]</i>with children;
    Let him be acceptable unto his brethren,
    And let him dip his foot in oil.
